Shutdown                    ----                 $  shutdown now


Install SublimeText         ----                 $  sudo apt-get update
                                                 $  sudo apt-get install sublime-text
                                                 
                                                 
Uninstall SublimeText       ----                 $  sudo apt-get remove sublime-text
                                                 $  sudo apt-get autoremove
                                                 
                                                 
Install Leafpad text editor ----                 $  sudo apt-get install leafpad


List directory contents     ----                 $  ls


Get list of all entered 
commands in terminal        ----                 $  history


Make new folder             ----                 $  mkdir ~/Downloads/new-folder
(Inside Downloads)
                                                 
                                                 
 Make new folder with       ----                 $  sudo mkdir ~/Downloads/new-folder
 write protected

Delete any folder           ----                 $  rm -R ~/Downloads/new-folder
                                                 
